'''代尔祖尔'''（{{lang-ar|دير الزور}}；[[阿拉米语|阿拉米语]]：ܕܝܪܐ ܙܥܘܪܬܐ, {{lang-hy|Տէր Զօր}}，{{lang|hy|Դեր Զոր}}，''Ter Zor''）也译为'''德尔祖尔'''，是[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]东北部城市，[[代尔祖尔省|代尔祖尔省]]省会。代尔祖尔地处叙利亚首都[[大马士革|大马士革]]东北450公里<ref name="tourism">{{cite web |title = Syrian Ministry of Tourism (in Arabic) |url = http://www.syriatourism.org/index.php?module=subjects&func=viewpage&pageid=2278 |accessdate = 2007-05-10 |archive-date = 2020-04-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200427130704/http://www.syriatourism.org/index.php?module=subjects&func=viewpage&pageid=2278 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]东南方320公里处的[[幼发拉底河|幼发拉底河]]河畔。经济以[[农业|农业]]为主。附近古迹众多，是著名的旅游胜地<ref>{{cite web| language =zh-hans| publisher =叙利亚旅游局| title =德尔祖尔| url =http://chinese.syriatourism.org/desert_7.htm| date =| accessdate =2011-08-25| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20111127064610/http://chinese.syriatourism.org/desert_7.htm| archivedate =2011-11-27}}</ref>。

從2015年3月起，代爾祖爾被恐怖組織[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]][[代爾祖爾之圍|長期圍攻]]，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3403857/The-town-20-people-day-die-starvation-200-000-Syrians-face-food-shortage-areas-siege-ISIS-government-forces.html |title=Picutres from Syria's Deir Ezzor under siege by ISIS show starving people |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2016-01-17 |accessdate=2016-10-05 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091529/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3403857/The-town-20-people-day-die-starvation-200-000-Syrians-face-food-shortage-areas-siege-ISIS-government-forces.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>城內的敘政府軍和20萬居民倚賴空運接濟。2017年9月，包圍圈外的敘政府軍成功打破包圍，代爾祖爾之圍結束。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria/syrian-army-allies-reach-airbase-besieged-by-islamic-state-in-eastern-syria-commander-idUSKCN1BK0IL |title=Syrian army, allies reach airbase besieged by Islamic State in eastern Syria: commander |publisher=Reuters |date=2017-09-09 |accessdate=2017-09-14 |archive-date=2017-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911070011/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria/syrian-army-allies-reach-airbase-besieged-by-islamic-state-in-eastern-syria-commander-idUSKCN1BK0IL |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==历史==
代尔祖尔在罗马时代是[[罗马帝国|罗马帝国]]和印度之间重要的贸易驿站，在这之后它被[[芝诺比阿|芝诺比阿]]征服，受[[巴尔米拉|巴尔米拉]]统治。后续一连串的征服战争使代尔祖尔饱受战争摧残，在[[蒙古帝国|蒙古]]横扫[[中东|中东]]时，代尔祖尔城被蒙古人摧毁了。

[[File:Armenian_Genocide_Museum_in_Der_Zor_Syria.jpg|thumb]]展览馆]]
1867年，[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]重建了代尔祖尔并进行了扩建。1915年，在[[亚美尼亚种族大屠杀|亚美尼亚种族大屠杀]]期间，这座城市成为[[亚美尼亚人|亚美尼亚人]][[死亡行进|死亡行进]]的主要目的地。<ref>{{cite book|author1=Fuat Dündar|editor1-last=Ronald Grigor Suny, Fatma Muge Gocek and Norman M. Naimark (Eds)|title=A Question of Genocide: Armenians and Turks at the End of the Ottoman Empire|date=2011|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=New York|ISBN=978-0-19-978104-1|pages=280-281|chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=q_mHshUAeZ8C&pg=PA280#v=onepage&q&f=false|chapter=Pouring a People into the Desert:The "Definitive Solution" of the Unionists to the Armenian Question|access-date=2017-11-04|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427130701/https://books.google.com/books?id=q_mHshUAeZ8C&pg=PA280#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1991年，代尔祖尔竖立起了这次事件的[[纪念碑|纪念碑]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.armenian-genocide.org/Memorial.110/current_category.72/memorials_detail.html|title=Monument and Memorial Complex at Der Zor, Syria|publisher=|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2011-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110805183244/http://www.armenian-genocide.org/Memorial.110/current_category.72/memorials_detail.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1921年，[[法兰西第三共和国|法国]]占领了代尔祖尔，使其成为一个大型驻军地点。与此同时，法国派一名贵族：哈吉-法德勒·阿布德（Haj-Fadel Abboud）管理该地。1941年，[[英国|英国]]军队在[[叙利亚-黎巴嫩战役|叙利亚-黎巴嫩战役]]中击败了[[维希法国|维希法国]]，其中有一场战斗就是在代尔祖尔进行的。之后他们将代尔祖尔转交给了[[自由法国|自由法国]]。1946年，代尔祖尔正式成为[[叙利亚共和国|叙利亚共和国]]的一部分。

自[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]爆发以来，[[叙利亚武装力量|叙利亚武装力量]]（政府军）和[[叙利亚自由军|叙利亚自由军]](反对派)以及其他组织(如[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]、[[征服沙姆阵线|征服沙姆阵线]])之间在代尔祖尔爆发了多次武装冲突。2014年9月21日，亚美尼亚人纪念碑被伊斯兰国武装分子炸毁。据调查，他们之前是征服沙姆阵线的成员。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hayrumyan|first1=Naira|title=Middle East Terror: Memory of Armenian Genocide victims targeted by ISIS militants|url=http://www.armenianow.com/commentary/analysis/57070/armenia_church_syria_isis_aram_catholicos|work=ArmeniaNow|date=24 September 2014|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905144120/http://www.armenianow.com/commentary/analysis/57070/armenia_church_syria_isis_aram_catholicos|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=IS said to destroy Armenian Genocide memorial|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/is-reportedly-destroys-armenian-genocide-memorial/|work=[[以色列时报|以色列时报]]|date=22 September 2014|accessdate=2017-11-04|archive-date=2018-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718145217/https://www.timesofisrael.com/is-reportedly-destroys-armenian-genocide-memorial/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Who destroyed the Armenian Genocide Martyrs’ Memorial Church in Deir Ezzor?|url=https://conflictantiquities.wordpress.com/2014/11/12/iraq-syria-islamic-state-destruction-deir-ez-zor-armenian-genocide-memorial-church-responsibility/|website=conflict antiquities|accessdate=20 March 2015|date=12 November 2014|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422231810/https://conflictantiquities.wordpress.com/2014/11/12/iraq-syria-islamic-state-destruction-deir-ez-zor-armenian-genocide-memorial-church-responsibility/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

代尔祖尔在两年多的时间里一直是叙利亚政府在叙利亚东部的少数几个军事据点之一。2015年5月，伊斯兰国武装分子发动进攻，占领了[[巴尔米拉|巴尔米拉]]，切断了通往代尔祖尔的陆上补给线。<ref name="siege">{{cite web|url=http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/100-000-civilians-under-isis-siege-in-deir-ez-zor/|title=100,000 Civilians under ISIS Siege in Eastern Syria|author=Chris Tomson|work=Al-Masdar News|date=12 December 2015|accessdate=12 December 2015|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331182724/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/100-000-civilians-under-isis-siege-in-deir-ez-zor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊斯兰国对代尔祖尔的围困使得代尔祖尔城的补给只能由[[运输直升机|运输直升机]]空投获得。<ref name="siege"/> 伊斯兰国试图通过袭击{{link-en|代尔祖尔机场|Deir ez-Zor Airport}}来阻止补给的输送。然而，他们的尝试失败了。在[[伊萨姆·扎赫雷丁|伊萨姆·扎赫雷丁]]少将领导下的[[叙利亚共和国卫队|叙利亚共和国卫队]]第104旅多次击败了来犯的武装分子。<ref name="siege"/> 

在2017年9月2日，来自[[苏赫奈|苏赫奈]]的一支{{link-en|叙利亚阿拉伯军|Syrian Army}}（SAA）军队到达代尔祖尔，开始进行解围行动。此后不久，伊斯兰国对代尔祖尔的围困正式解除。<ref>{{cite news|title=First scenes from the Syrian Army’s lifting of the Deir Ezzor siege|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/first-scenes-syrian-armys-lifting-deir-ezzor-siege/|agency=Al Masdar|date=5 September 2017|accessdate=6 September 2017|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803113552/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/first-scenes-syrian-armys-lifting-deir-ezzor-siege/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2017年11月3日，SAA完全解放了代尔祖尔。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-fully-liberates-deir-ezzor-city/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-11-04 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924121652/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-fully-liberates-deir-ezzor-city/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

